"{\"uid\": \"nbcnewyork.com-news-local-olympic-chocolate-muffins-nyc-line-5733925\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics may have discovered a tasty new event thanks to Henrik Christiansen.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 72, \"end\": 91, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.6621615443867334, \"rank\": 0.5102040816327192, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Norwegian swimmer has found unexpected TikTok fame due to his obsession with the chocolate muffins at Olympic village.\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.8851174089055863, \"rank\": 0.06290606794923236, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9872105089844738e-36, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What would you do for a chocolate muffin?\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what independent designer Kelin Carolyn Zhang asked herself as she watched Norwegian swimmerHenrik Christiansenproclaim his love for the chocolate muffins served in the Olympic Village on TikTok.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\", \"score\": 0.485755301837569, \"rank\": 0.831831005395507, \"text\": \"Carolyn\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\"}, {\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.8851174089055863, \"rank\": 0.06290606794923236, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4856312033474886e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 455, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9872105089844738e-36, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christiansen posted over a dozen videos about his beloved \\\"choccy muffin,\\\" and Olympic stars like \\\"Pommel horse guy\\\"Stephen Nedoroscikand track and field gold medalistGabby Thomasalso shared their love for the baked good.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC 4 free wherever you are  The single greatest thing about the Olympic Village so far\\ud83e\\udd24#fyp#muffins#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage  Zhang was intrigued.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999957184359828, \"rank\": 4.188567417862527e-06, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4856312033474886e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three weeks later, she tracked down the French supplier, facilitated a shipment of muffins to the U.S. and dealt with the resulting challenges, all to bring the viral muffins to New York City for a pop-up event.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9979082742985469, \"rank\": 0.0017597423163227433, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.287700913925546e-14, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a thread on X, Zhangdetailedhow she worked with New York City cafeIsshiki Matchato bring the viral muffins to hundreds of New Yorkers on Aug. 17.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.287700913925546e-14, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a big believer in just trying new things,\\\" Zhang told NBC News.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1288, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9974381630464872, \"rank\": 0.0023242798618701515, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think this was one of the more extreme examples of that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her viral quest for the muffins began: she produced and posted several videos trying to identify the creator of the muffins.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She eventuallydiscoveredthat they were made by Coup de pates.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Around then, a stranger commented that her friend Angel Zheng, the owner of Isshiki Matcha, would be willing to help her import and sell the muffins.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.5871188823853069, \"rank\": 0.6452633020106462, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}, {\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999997383079404, \"rank\": 2.402909493959567e-07, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}, {\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matcha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"i decide to procrastinate on work and track down who made these muffinsi post a couple of tiktoks evaluating different options that i had seen mentioned online: otis spunkmeyer, delifrance, coup de pates(this was over ~6hrs on tue 7/30 evening)https://t.co/Y1MzBYEFYw  \\\"I think I am the only crazy cafe owner in New York City that would agree to such a short amount of time to do something at this capacity,\\\" Zheng said in an interview with NBC News.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2012, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.287700913925546e-14, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.5871188823853069, \"rank\": 0.6452633020106462, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}, {\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9974381630464872, \"rank\": 0.0023242798618701515, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Isshiki Matcha, which has been open for four months, primarily sells premium matcha and matcha drinks.\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999997383079404, \"rank\": 2.402909493959567e-07, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matcha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng described her interest in bringing authentic food to bigger audiences and doing events like the collaboration with Zhang or fashion pop-ups.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.5871188823853069, \"rank\": 0.6452633020106462, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her thread, Zhang detailed the obstacles she faced in securing the muffins, including: having to reach out to Coup de pates on multiple platforms, getting customs and FDA approval and worrying about the muffins spoiling.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2573, \"end\": 2576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.904458133785356e-28, \"text\": \"FDA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the muffins arrived in the U.S., the customs broker told Zhang that they could not be delivered the day of because the refrigerated truck was too small.\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The broker offered to ask the airline to store the muffins in a freezer until the next morning and then eventually was able to deliver the same day.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng even bought a new freezer to store the muffins.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.5871188823853069, \"rank\": 0.6452633020106462, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang described her mindset throughout as focusing on one problem at a time and being solution-oriented.\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The day of the event, hundreds of New Yorkerslined upstarting at 6 a.m. to buy a muffin.\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After eating some themselves and sharing with family and friends, the duo sold the remaining 263 muffins.\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The cafepricedeach muffin at $10, and Zheng said that most of that went to transport costs and they primarily made money that day when customers bought a matcha alongside the muffin.\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3330, \"end\": 3335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.5871188823853069, \"rank\": 0.6452633020106462, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some online have criticized the hype over a simple muffin, Zhang said that it was lighthearted fun that allowed fans watching the Olympics from a continent away to feel included.\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not be an Olympic athlete,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could eat this viral muffin that all these Olympic athletes can not stop talking about.\\\"\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang described the muffin as light, moist and not too sweet.\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a fan,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she was only able to eat three-quarters of a muffin, mostly for a taste test that she posted online, and hopes to try more.\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 4018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang and Zheng are trying to import another batch of muffins to sell (and eat), but nothing has been finalized yet.\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4031, \"end\": 4036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.5871188823853069, \"rank\": 0.6452633020106462, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, what Zhang has cherished the most is the experience.\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Have fun - life is short,\\\" Zhang said.\", \"from\": 4198, \"to\": 4237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Be a little silly.\\\"\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4258, \"entities\": []}]}"